    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Halloween Trouble 6: Pumpkin Rampage</strong> is a spooky Match-3 puzzle that follows the adventures of the witch, Ronida. When a magical battle with a wizard goes awry, it causes the magic creatures of the swamp to run amok, threatening the peaceful town of Jamberton! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the witch as she chases one adventure after another, Enjoy the varied Match-3 levels as you visit different locations. <i>Play minigames such as Jigsaw, Sliders, Solitaire, and Hidden object.</i> Take quests from the residents of Jamberton and solve them as you enjoy the Halloween themed artwork and music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you help Ronida stop the pumpkin rampage and save Jamberton?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 challenging Match-3 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of minigames: Jigsaw, Slider, Solitaire, and Hidden Object</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging storyline with colorful characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable gameplay options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautifully crafted Halloween-themed visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collector's Edition includes bonus campaign with 61 extra levels</p></li></ul>",
